7:35:30.000Z","msg":"亂入<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港島區濕鳩踢波group<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/FV0IuQtEOk9ha9eqz1tyDw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FFV0IuQtEOk9ha9eqz1tyDw&d=JAxdhPRnajumMRT%2BlKiLaG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=6b484c8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/FV0IuQtEOk9ha9eqz1tyDw</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a3289caf9c5783f9c33f38b335971940ff5f8bb","tid":356650,"uid":92200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:02:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔會再信任何聲稱新手足球gp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依句真</blockquote><br />\n我敢講，全世界得我呢隊係真新手足球Group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隊波上年係高登組成，真係雜牌軍<br />\n但每個月都會定期踢1,2次，咁進步實有架啦<br />\n但唔會勁到踢得好勁，同埋我地都唔需要咁勁，因為都係至在做運動<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 入過黎既巴打都無一個因為我地唔係新手而走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae255fdff95289adb15a7f2626cd142bfa2c217","tid":356650,"uid":92200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:02:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>填唔到form</blockquote><br />\n+1</blockquote><br />\nE...點解咁..我處理下先"},{"pid":"7cdc7e334bf3016722c90bd25ee6e431abc9180c","tid":356650,"uid":92200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:02:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係九龍流浪 ?</blockquote><br />\n咩黎?"},{"pid":"680820987be9b90899388a083c1f6bca7668ad6b","tid":356650,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:03:49.000Z","msg":"出到黎成班屈哂機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2269613d76adba9c19b253a6dedc9a77ef45f800","tid":356650,"uid":35193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:04:37.000Z","msg":"出到黎個個甲組實力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e974f21ef9b723bb585e0b7e2dc4a7b77f0d1893","tid":356650,"uid":92200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:06:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出到黎成班屈哂機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我再講多D喇消除大家懷疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係社工黎，亦都係一個踢波廢柴  但我自己就好鐘意踢波<br />\n咁我上左高登咁耐，都知唔少人中伏入D勁GROUP<br />\n加上踢波又要場地 又要夾時間  令到好多巴打想踢下都難<br />\n<br />\n咁我就試下攪隊波真係至在踢波 過下癮~<br />\n本身得1X個  呢家踢左一年 , 已經4X個<br />\n但真係有好多巴打要返工返學夾唔到時間<br />\n所以先再招多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"108d6aa59e0ad01c05296c9843d53cc155232d82","tid":356650,"uid":92200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:08:47.000Z","msg":"份表應該填到架啦"},{"pid":"f068c30b8cab5394f3fd480e5cce84f38b830b60","tid":356650,"uid":3480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:24:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>份表應該填到架啦</blockquote><br />\n填唔到"},{"pid":"08dcdd0467120ad45f1429268246513146aacd88","tid":356650,"uid":92200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:30:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>份表應該填到架啦</blockquote><br />\n填唔到</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdIXO6DEzAfgKHQrvGONDSdA7nBrDpQPso-GCJ8SJSoAO07Tw/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdIXO